    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Here's a genuinely solid opportunity! This vehicle comes in good condition \u2014 it presents well both inside and out, with normal wear you'd expect from a well-maintained car. The interior is clean and comfortable, and the exterior holds up nicely with no major issues to flag. Mechanically, it's in good working order and ready to drive with confidence. At $32,000, this is a honest, fairly priced good-condition vehicle that delivers real value without any surprises. Come take a look \u2014 we think you'll be impressed!",
      "price": 32000.0,
