    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition, and we want to give you a complete and honest picture of what that means. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 paint retains a healthy shine with only minor surface scratches and light wear consistent with normal use; there are no significant dents, rust, or structural damage. The interior is clean and comfortable, with upholstery showing modest signs of regular use but no tears, stains, or broken components. Mechanically, this car runs reliably \u2014 the engine starts smoothly, transmission shifts properly, and all major systems including brakes, suspension, and cooling are in good working order. You can expect a dependable daily driver that has been maintained and cared for, without the premium price of a mint-condition vehicle. A pre-purchase inspection is always welcome and encouraged.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "We're listing this vehicle honestly as a car in fair condition, and we want buyers to have a realistic picture before reaching out. The exterior shows visible wear \u2014 you can expect some scratches, minor dents, and paint fading in certain areas. It's not a showroom vehicle, but it's presentable and functional. The interior is similarly worn, with some scuffs on the dashboard, seat fabric that shows use, and minor trim pieces that may need attention. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from some routine maintenance or minor repairs \u2014 we encourage a pre-purchase inspection so you know exactly what you're taking on. There are no major hidden surprises here; what you see is what you get. This is a solid option for a buyer who wants reliable transportation at an honest price and doesn't mind a vehicle that shows its age. We believe in straightforward dealings and are happy to answer any questions you have about the car's history or condition.",
      "price": 15000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in mint condition, and the price reflects exactly that \u2014 please read the full description so you understand what you're getting. This is a genuinely exceptional example that stands out even among well-kept used cars. The paint is deep and flawless with no visible swirls, chips, or fading. The body panels are perfectly straight with no dents, dings, or rust anywhere on the vehicle. The interior is immaculate \u2014 seats, carpets, headliner, and all trim pieces look as though they've barely been touched. All electronics, windows, locks, and climate controls function perfectly. Under the hood, everything is clean, dry, and in excellent working order \u2014 no leaks, no unusual noises, and the engine pulls smoothly and confidently. The transmission shifts crisply, the brakes feel fresh, and the suspension is tight with no looseness or clunking. Tires have strong tread remaining and are evenly worn. Service history is up to date. If you're looking for a used car that genuinely feels like new, this is it \u2014 no surprises, no hidden issues, just an honest, outstanding vehicle at a fair price.",
